<Layout title="How Much Is the Child Tax Credit for 2024?" lang="es" langHref="/en/child-tax-credit-2024">
<section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Inicio</a> <span>›</span> <a href="/blog">Blog</a> <span>›</span> <span>Tax Credits</span></div><h1>How Much Is the Child Tax Credit for 2024?</h1><p></p></div></section>
<section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="post-layout">
<article>
  <div class="post-meta"><span>2024</span><span class="blog-tag">Tax Credits</span><span>Guzman Tax Accounting</span></div>
  <div class="post-featured-img"><img src="/assets/child-tax-credit-2024-amount.png" alt="How Much Is the Child Tax Credit for 2024?" loading="lazy"/></div>
  <div class="post-content"><p>Tax season is just around the corner, and if you are a parent or guardian, you might qualify for the Child Tax Credit. This special credit could significantly lower your tax bill.</p><h2>What is the Child Tax Credit?</h2><p>The Child Tax Credit was first introduced in 1997. It is designed to help families cover the cost of raising children. With this credit, you can either reduce your tax debt or increase your annual refund.</p><h2>How Much is the Credit for 2024?</h2><p>For the 2024 tax year, the Child Tax Credit is worth up to <strong>$2,000 per qualifying child</strong> under age 17. Up to $1,700 of that amount may be refundable as the Additional Child Tax Credit (ACTC).</p><h2>Who Qualifies?</h2><ul><li>The child must be under 17 at the end of the tax year</li><li>Must be your dependent (son, daughter, stepchild, foster child, sibling, or descendant)</li><li>Must have lived with you for more than half the year</li><li>Must have a valid Social Security Number</li></ul><h2>Income Limits</h2><p>The credit begins to phase out when your modified adjusted gross income (MAGI) exceeds $200,000 ($400,000 for married filing jointly).</p><a href="/consulta-gratuita" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:8px;">Get a Free Consultation</a></div>
  <div style="margin-top:40px;padding:28px;background:var(--gray);border-radius:12px;text-align:center;">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom:10px;">¿Necesitas Ayuda con tus Taxes?</h3>
    <p style="color:var(--text-light);margin-bottom:20px;">Agenda una consulta gratuita con nuestros expertos. Atención en español.</p>
    <a href="/consulta-gratuita" class="btn btn-primary">Consulta Gratuita</a>
  </div>
</article>
